      "\u003cp\u003eNexient: React Native Developer\nYou're a dreamer. Passionate about mobile development and writing efficient code. Someone who can see the finished product before development has started. You're able to take client requirements, and then work with a team to translate those into user stories that can be implemented.\nWe're Nexient; we've expanded our footprint with a brand-new product development center, located here in the heart of the Buckeye State - Columbus, Ohio.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAt Nexient, we bring a “Product Mindset” to our work; using small teams and Agile thinking to build great custom software people love to use. As America's leading 100% US, 100% Agile software services partner, we're building it here – in Columbus, Ohio, instead of sending tech jobs offshore.\nWe're looking for an experienced React Native Developer to join our team here in Columbus to develop applications for both iOS and Android.\nYou've got 8 years of experience in software development experience; 5 years' using Mobile/JavaScript/UI technologies, with 2 years' in React Native. An understanding of REST Web Services, JSON and Design Patterns.\nSound like you? Come build with us!\nDon't just dream about What's Next – build it!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eApply Here: \u003ca href=\"https://www.click2apply.net/b7sgjxt8yyfqc878\"\u003ehttps://www.click2apply.net/b7sgjxt8yyfqc878\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePI115266789\u003c/p\u003e\n",
