    description:
      "\u003cp\u003eAll of us rely on software in some form in our everyday lives. At some point, inevitably, software applications can and do malfunction. It's not just homes that need built on a good foundation. That's where you come into play, software engineer.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIn this day and age with technology booming, that's where we step in.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe're Nexient; we've expanded our footprint with a brand-new product development center, located here in the heart of the Buckeye State - Columbus, Ohio.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAt Nexient, we bring a “Product Mindset” to our work; using small teams and Agile thinking to build great custom software people love to use. As America's leading 100% US, 100% Agile software services partner, we're building it here – in Columbus, Ohio, instead of sending tech jobs offshore.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIf you've got 5+ years' experience in programming primarily around JavaScript, HTML \u0026amp; CSS, are experienced in object-oriented design, have expertise in writing and consuming web services, and have been hands on with frameworks like React.js in an Agile environment – come build with us!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe're looking for an experienced JavaScript engineer who can understand client requirements and translate those into software applications, while leading a small team of developers.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDon't just dream about what's next – build it!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eApply Here: \u003ca href=\"http://www.Click2Apply.net/c4ksjqdb48pjjzdj\"\u003ehttp://www.Click2Apply.net/c4ksjqdb48pjjzdj\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePI115161594\u003c/p\u003e\n",
