    description:
      '\u003cp\u003eWe are 100% part of BNP Paribas Group and one of 13 BNP Paribas corporations. Due to sustainable growth, within 15 years we have established ourselves as one of the leading providers of consumer credits on the German market. At the same time, we have reacted to the mega trend of digitalization early on, putting a strong focus on extending our online- and E-Commerce business. Our mission is to support our partners with innovative products and processes, and to stand by our customers’ side with fair financing offers to help them realize their wishes.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAre you looking for a new challenge and would like to contribute to the success story of Consors Finanz? Then the following position in Munich might be the right one for you:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eJAVA Software Developer (m/f/d)\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eYour Major Job Functions:\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIn your position as JAVA Software Developer, you are becoming a valuable part of our company. The develop leader of the digital factory is in charge of defining and maintaining the coherence of the developments of its digital factory, both on the choice of technologies in connection with the community of the digital factory and on the quality of the developments produced by the Teams.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eYou will create and develop object-oriented and technologically advanced Java EE applications\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eYou will also be responsible for testing, commissioning and maintaining the developed systems\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRegular proactive involvement in requirements specifications and coordination with other specialist departments, as well as an estimate of the development effort, round off your exciting field of activity\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eYour Human Capital:\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eYou have a university degree in computer science, business informatics or economics with a focus on computer science\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eYou have extensive operational project experience in object-oriented programming and design\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eYou have very good Java knowledge and solid experience with JEE or EJB3/Hibernate\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eYou have already worked in web development with JSP/JSF/Vaadin, also worked with SQL/Oracle, SOAP/REST, Maven, GIT, JBoss and are familiar with object orientation concepts and design patterns\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eA very good knowledge of written and spoken English is required\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eYou feel comfortable in a dynamic, international environment, are flexible and have strong analytical skills\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eA high degree of quality and customer orientation rounds off your competent profile\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eYour Benefits:\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOccupational pension provision in the form of a membership in BVV Bankenversicherung (bank insurance)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFlexible working hours in the form of various part-time models and autonomous working time arrangements\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eA dynamic and agile working environment, short decision-making paths and a familiar working atmosphere\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSupport for your professional and personal development with extensive in-house training courses\nFree WLAN at the locations, which may be used privately within reasonable limits\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eDo you think you would be a good fit?\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThen become part of the BNP Paribas Group and shape your future with us! We look forward to receiving your application with your notice period and salary expectations via the \u003cstrong\u003eApplication form\u003c/strong\u003e or our online portal.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href="https://bnpparibas.redirect.your-jobresponse.com/java_software_developer_m_w_d_muenchen/257627/V819/anwenden"\u003eClick here for the application form!\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eConsors Finanz\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eElisabeth Blau /HR Business Management\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href="http://www.consorsfinanz.de"\u003ewww.consorsfinanz.de\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n',
