    title: "Senior Front End Developer",
    description:
      '\u003cp\u003eWhat are you going to do?\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWatch our video: \u003ca href="https://youtu.be/wf8drvVRgp4"\u003ehttps://youtu.be/wf8drvVRgp4\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePon Digital Solutions invents, designs and builds digital solutions for the Pon brands; from Gazelle and Caterpillar to Skoda and Volkswagen. We are building integrations, APIs, mobile apps, IoT solutions and websites, among other things. Our goal? Stimulate and realize digital innovation within Pon!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAs a senior front-end developer you daily develop modern, creative and functional front-end applications that really make a difference and are used by large groups of end users. You also help and coach junior front-end developers.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBefore a project starts, you and your team choose the technologies that you want to use (you can of course substantiate this choice well). When making the code you build "reusable high performance code" and share it, together with your knowledge, with your colleagues.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIn addition to the projects you will be working on, you contribute to Pon Digital Solutions: a start-up within a corporate environment. The team consists of a group of enthusiastic specialists and developers. Real professionals with whom you can spar.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAnd yes, we work fully Agile, based on scrum and have an innovation day every month where we work on our own innovative solutions.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhat do we ask?\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTo successfully perform this role, it is important that you are a passionate developer: you get energy from building beautiful solutions. You are constantly learning and keeping the community in good spirits.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe also ask:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eknowledge of (one of) the latest technologies (React Native, Angular 2+, Vue JS, Node, Webpack, CI / CD);\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eexperience as a front-end developer (at least 6 years);\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eaffinity with coaching to support junior developers where necessary;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003euse common sense to find the best solutions for customers.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhat do we offer?\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIn addition to working among the most beautiful cars all day, you and your team also have time to innovate and you can grow into a full stack developer whenever you want.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMake it Fun is one of our core values and you can count on excellent working conditions at Pon:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ea (more than) competitive salary with a good bonus scheme\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCYD: choose your device (laptop and telephone) yourself\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e33 vacation days and the possibility to buy extra\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIndividual choice of budget (that includes the value of extra statutory leave and and 8% holiday bonus)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ea good Pon pension plan\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ea collective health insurance policy with a large contribution from Pon\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePon Fit: participate in boot camps, cycling and cycling rounds, running events, hockey, golf clinics and much more\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eContact information\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAre you still reading? You can send your resume and motivation directly by clicking on "Apply Direct" on the following website: \u003ca href="https://www.jobsatpon.com/?search=developer\u0026amp;panel=application_detail\u0026amp;application_id=1040954"\u003ehttps://www.jobsatpon.com/?search=developer\u0026amp;panel=application_detail\u0026amp;application_id=1040954\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDo you have any questions? Please contact Gabriella Serreli at 06-53927769 or \u003ca href="mailto:gabriella.serreli@pon.com"\u003egabriella.serreli@pon.com\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eApplication procedure\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIf you have applied, you will receive a response from us quickly. The first interview is with one of our front end developers. You then do an assessment where one of the team leads. If that is good, you will receive a proposal from us the next day at the latest.\u003c/p\u003e\n',
