      "\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSenior Full Stack Engineer\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAJ Madison is looking for a \u003cstrong\u003eSenior / Lead Full Stack Engineer\u003c/strong\u003e who’s a true technophile, an independent thinker, and a strong team player to lead our web engineering team.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis is a critical leadership position.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDesigning and developing systems and applications, making specific determinations about system performance.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDesign and develop fault-tolerant scalable systems.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDesigning and developing next-gen architecture (web, mobile etc.).\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAJ Madison prides itself on its innovative and knowledgeable staff. Our team members are not just sales associates; they are passionate chefs, laundry enthusiasts, and design aficionados. Our mission is to leverage the unique talents and passions of our employees to inspire, delight, and enrich the lives of each of our customers. Through the usage of the latest technology, product knowledge and passion for the industry, we at AJ Madison have been successful at providing the best experience possible for each of customers. If you have a passion and curiosity for what is possible and enjoy people, we invite you to join us on our mission.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat You’ll Do\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWork on a cross-functional team of other engineers (frontend, backend, and full stack), a Product Manager and a Designer.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWork on our production application – a PHP and MySql app with React/Redux on the frontend.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eShip new experiences to our customers via A/B tests.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDeploy to code to production multiple times a day.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHelp us figure out engineering solutions that give 80% of the benefit with 20% of the work.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWrite automated functional and unit tests.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eYou..\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHave at least 7+ years of full stack experience. Minimum 3 years' experience developing rich, large-scale web applications (prerebaly ecommerce applications).\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHave seen what works well and what doesn’t work well in frontend and backend codebases.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAre an expert in one server language, (preferably PHP), Javascript and one frontend framework (preferably React).\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLike being part of a small team composed of UX designers, product managers, frontend/backend/full stack engineers.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAre excited to teach and learn from those around you.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWe..\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAre a collaborative \u0026amp; close-knit team: our team is Brooklyn-based and in the office because as great as technology is, there are few substitutes for in-person collaboration.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTake pride in our work and shares responsibility to see it through from conception to deployment to fixing bugs.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCan offer you top of the line equipment: your choice of hardware, standing desks, two 4K monitors, and more.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOffer a competitive compensation and benefits package.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eValue honesty, transparency and respect.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAre excited to hear from you.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n",
